{"tid":1415053,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好意思，各位手足麻煩入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T13:31:41.000Z","uid":177824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"354cabfc42191483af00239c0ebaded3acaedf44","tid":1415053,"uid":177824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:08:37.000Z","msg":"先講明放核彈都絕不割席，但完全感覺到部分人開始失控，容易傷及無辜同屌錯人。<br />\n<br />\n希望所有發夢嘅人謹守三大原則：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">針對政權</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以禮待人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人不犯我 我不犯人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n對於班狗，想點就點唔好殺人就得。對於平民百姓影相，由佢哋影，或者禮貌咁樣叫佢哋熄電話，唔好呼喝佢哋。對於反對者，由佢地講，除非對方出手唔係都唔好還拖。<br />\n<br />\n仲有最重要掛兩句說話喺嘴邊：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好意思</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">麻煩哂你</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好一黎有乜不滿就屌人老母，了解左情況先，唔係街坊鄰居見到觀感會好差。<br />\n<br />\n其次係今日扔野入紀律部隊宿舍！入面有自己友架，唔好令自己盟友受害，要扔就扔得狗嘅狗籠！<br />\n<br />\n最後文宣方面，噴乜寫乜都冇問題，但記得唔好去屋苑地方咁做！屋苑地方痴紙就好啦，一嚟大家嘅設計有美感同時吸睛，但就咁畫野佢哋會感覺冇咁好。<br />\n <br />\n冇錯呢一刻民意仍然支持我地，但我地都要保持著民意，唔好比自己同班狗仲有黑社會同水平！保持冷靜，唔好比怒火沖上腦隨意破壞，針對返目標行動。<br />\n<br />\n就系咁多，光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"5e8d40ad832fc08f9404777da494eb4745efdf6f","tid":1415053,"uid":177824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:10:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17129f625ae0302017091d469de0e343420700ae","tid":1415053,"uid":177824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:11:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fc9526f1d4618760577475e3666bd486598fe98a","tid":1415053,"uid":177824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:11:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"56872ea9ef3226258bdef026e9dbf838b0496418","tid":1415053,"uid":177824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:12:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7d6837a7e611fadebd2bf82ec6e7d2355bd60e96","tid":1415053,"uid":177824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:13:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"549bfb715052a12c84c1765f2653cb5d7d98a442","tid":1415053,"uid":177824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:14:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a1584be7b8c1c86fe7f7f4d46c56fb8c38671786","tid":1415053,"uid":177824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:16:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"53b8a47d236c204fc4ab7021c61fef44b81b8b6e","tid":1415053,"uid":177824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:16:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5b0a89b7c490e772d8680f3e91aa2de9d9fdc93e","tid":1415053,"uid":177824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:18:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"06806a8c5b570ad8bd4439e0c121de5fd2464a9e","tid":1415053,"uid":177824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:21:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d1bb3e9e248ca15e2a69210eca470dd360e11736","tid":1415053,"uid":177824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:22:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"29760b67d056e90c67c46233540c583ee5c62bc9","tid":1415053,"uid":177824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:27:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5140429686379e03f9621d55276c75170ce858af","tid":1415053,"uid":177824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:31:41.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}